<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="es">
<head>
    <%- include('partials/head', { 
        title: 'Comedor de los Pobres - Contáctanos', 
        description: 'Contáctanos. Asociación Juan XXIII - Comedor de los Pobres. Ponte en comunicación con nosotros para donar o ser voluntario.' 
    }) %>
    <style>
        .hero-contact {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #f5f3ff 0%, #ffffff 100%);
            border-radius: 0 0 4rem 4rem;
            box-shadow: 0 10px 30px rgba(124, 58, 237, 0.05);
            border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(124, 58, 237, 0.04);
        }

        .input-field {
            width: 100%;
            padding: 1rem 1.5rem;
            background: #ffffff;
            border: 2px solid #f1f5f9;
            border-radius: 1rem;
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
            outline: none;
        }

        .input-field:focus {
            border-color: var(--morado);
            box-shadow: 0 0 0 4px rgba(124, 58, 237, 0.1);
        }

        .contact-card {
            background: white;
            padding: 2.5rem;
            border-radius: 2.5rem;
            box-shadow: 0 10px 30px rgba(0,0,0,0.02);
        }

        .map-container {
            border-radius: 2.5rem;
            overflow: hidden;
            box-shadow: 0 20px 40px rgba(0,0,0,0.05);
            border: 8px solid white;
        }

        .card-hover {
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
        }

        .card-hover:hover {
            transform: translateY(-10px);
            box-shadow: 0 25px 50px -12px rgba(124, 58, 237, 0.25);
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

    <!-- NAVBAR-->
    <%- include('partials/navbar') %>

    <!-- PORTADA -->
    <header class="hero-contact pt-20 pb-24 text-center">
        <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-6">
            <span class="text-orange-500 font-black text-[10px] uppercase tracking-widest mb-4 block">Estamos para escucharte</span>
            <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-black text-purple-900 mb-6">Contáctanos</h1>
            <p class="text-gray-500 text-lg leading-relaxed max-w-2xl mx-auto">
                ¿Tienes dudas, quieres ser voluntario o realizar una donación en especie? Envíanos un mensaje y nos pondremos en contacto contigo.
            </p>
        </div>
    </header>

    <!-- SECCIÓN FORMULARIO Y MAPA -->
    <section class="pt-16 pb-16">
        <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6">
            
            <div class="grid lg:grid-cols-12 gap-12">
                
                <!-- Columna Formulario -->
                <div class="lg:col-span-7">
                    <div class="contact-card">
                        <h2 class="text-2xl font-black text-purple-900 mb-8">Envía un mensaje</h2>
                        
                        <form action="#" class="space-y-6">
                            <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-6">
                                <div>
                                    <label class="text-[10px] font-black text-gray-400 uppercase block mb-2 ml-1">Nombre Completo</label>
                                    <input type="text" class="input-field" placeholder="Ej. Juan Pérez">
                                </div>
                                <div>
                                    <label class="text-[10px] font-black text-gray-400 uppercase block mb-2 ml-1">Correo Electrónico</label>
                                    <input type="email" class="input-field" placeholder="ejemplo@correo.com">
                                </div>
                            </div>
                            
                            <div>
                                <label class="text-[10px] font-black text-gray-400 uppercase block mb-2 ml-1">Asunto</label>
                                <input type="text" class="input-field" placeholder="¿En qué podemos ayudarte?">
                            </div>

                            <div>
                                <label class="text-[10px] font-black text-gray-400 uppercase block mb-2 ml-1">Mensaje</label>
                                <textarea class="input-field h-40 resize-none" placeholder="Escribe aquí tus comentarios..."></textarea>
                            </div>

                            <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row items-center justify-between gap-6 pt-4">
                                <!-- Placeholder para el ReCAPTCHA -->
                                <div class="bg-gray-50 px-4 py-3 rounded-xl border border-gray-100 flex items-center gap-4 w-full md:w-auto">
                                    <div class="w-6 h-6 border-2 border-gray-300 rounded"></div>
                                    <span class="text-sm text-gray-500 font-medium">No soy un robot</span>
                                    <i class="fas fa-shield-alt text-gray-300 ml-4"></i>
                                </div>

                                <button type="submit" class="w-full md:w-auto px-10 py-4 bg-purple-600 text-white rounded-full font-black text-sm hover:bg-purple-700 transition shadow-xl shadow-purple-100 uppercase tracking-widest">
                                    Enviar Formulario
                                </button>
                            </div>
                        </form>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <!-- Columna Info de Contacto Rápido -->
                <div class="lg:col-span-5 space-y-6">
                    <div class="bg-purple-900 rounded-[2.5rem] p-10 text-white relative overflow-hidden">
                        <div class="relative z-10">
                            <h3 class="text-xl font-black mb-6">Canales Directos</h3>
                            <div class="space-y-6">
                                <div class="flex items-start gap-4">
                                    <div class="w-10 h-10 bg-purple-800 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center shrink-0">
                                        <i class="fas fa-phone-alt text-orange-400"></i>
                                    </div>
                                    <div>
                                        <span class="text-[10px] font-bold text-purple-300 uppercase block mb-1">Teléfono Oficinas</span>
                                        <p class="font-bold text-lg"><a href="tel:8183751163" class="hover:text-orange-400 transition-colors">81 8375 1163</a></p>
                                    </div>
                                    <div class="w-10 h-10 bg-purple-800 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center shrink-0 ml-8 sm:ml-12">
                                        <i class="fab fa-whatsapp text-orange-400 text-lg"></i>
                                    </div>
                                    <div>
                                        <span class="text-[10px] font-bold text-purple-300 uppercase block mb-1">Whatsapp</span>
                                        <p class="font-bold text-lg"><a href="https://wa.me/528130954567" target="_blank" class="hover:text-orange-400 transition-colors">81 3095 4567</a></p>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                                <div class="flex items-start gap-4">
                                    <div class="w-10 h-10 bg-purple-800 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center shrink-0">
                                        <i class="fas fa-envelope text-orange-400"></i>
                                    </div>
                                    <div>
                                        <span class="text-[10px] font-bold text-purple-300 uppercase block mb-1">Correo General</span>
                                        <p class="font-bold"><a href="mailto:unete@comedordelospobres.org" class="hover:text-orange-400 transition-colors">unete@comedordelospobres.org</a></p>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <!-- Decoración -->
                        <div class="absolute -right-10 -bottom-10 w-40 h-40 bg-purple-800 rounded-full opacity-50"></div>
                    </div>

                    <div class="bg-white rounded-[2.5rem] p-10 border border-gray-100">
                        <h3 class="text-purple-900 font-black mb-6">Nuestras Sedes</h3>
                        <div class="space-y-4">
                            <div class="flex items-center gap-3 text-sm text-gray-600">
                                <i class="fas fa-check text-green-500"></i> Monterrey (Oficina Administrativa)
                            </div>
                            <div class="flex items-center gap-3 text-sm text-gray-600">
                                <i class="fas fa-check text-green-500"></i> Escobedo
                            </div>
                            <div class="flex items-center gap-3 text-sm text-gray-600">
                                <i class="fas fa-check text-green-500"></i> García
                            </div>
                            <div class="flex items-center gap-3 text-sm text-gray-600">
                                <i class="fas fa-check text-green-500"></i> Guadalupe
                            </div>
                            <div class="flex items-center gap-3 text-sm text-gray-600">
                                <i class="fas fa-check text-green-500"></i> Juárez
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>

            </div>

                    </div>
    </section>

    <!-- FOOTER -->
    <%- include('partials/footer') %>
</body>
</html>